_sText: Notice that this map wasn't tested due computer problems so please leave a feedback after you played in the map. Thanks! This is a version from the map Urbanwar by Arnaud. 1 Open the 'Steam' folder 2 Then 'steammaps'. 3 Now open the folder with your Steam username. 4 and next 'counterstrike source' or 'counterstrike source beta' folder. 5 The open the 'cstrike' folder then 'maps'. 6 Extract the bsp file. 7 copy the bsp file. 8 Paste it on the 'maps' folder. 9 Launch the game. 10 ENJOY! This map is for free use on any server as long as you agree to: -Not decompile this map!
